    "body": "Problem: `make_floating_popup_options` used `wincol` to determine horizontal anchor,  When relative is editor the anchor should not depend on cursor position.\r\n\r\nSolution: Force anchor='W' when `relative='editor'`.\r\n\r\nFix #39306 \r\nFix #39307\r\nClose https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/39309\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-22T13:17:05Z",
    "comment_data": [],
    "comment_regular_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "thought about it carefully, and I don’t think it’s worth opening a PR just to fix these two issues. `g:style` is inherently a temporary thing. `:float` modifier #31902 and previewpopup #26799  should probably be moved forward instead. I’ll revisit #26799 these days..",
