            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> `g:style` is inherently a temporary thing. `:float` modifier #31902 and previewpopup #26799 should probably be moved forward instead.\r\n\r\n@glepnir thanks for considering that. this PR looks pretty minimal though, and `make_floating_popup_options` is used by more than just health, right? Also, refining the behavior of `make_floating_popup_options` and `open_floating_preview` (like in https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/38724 ), does help us build a \"spec\" for https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/25514 .",
